$ SQLite: drop table
@ drop table

{ Dropping a table if it exists

  In order to suppress error messages, → development/databases/SQLite supports the `drop table if exists` clause which only tries to drop a table if it in fact *does* exist:
  gh|about-sqlite|/tables/drop_if_exists.sql||


}

